rows.label: qst202717_0010
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]This is bad...

rows.label: qst202717_0020
rows.name: What's bad?

rows.label: qst202717_0030
rows.name:
This ritual is different from the others. It seems they're
planning to summon something seriously dangerous.

rows.label: qst202717_0040
rows.name: It looks the same as always, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202717_0050
rows.name:
But something inside
me is telling me so.

rows.label: qst202717_0060
rows.name:
Let's trust Mei. We need
to stop them immediately.

rows.label: qst202717_0070
rows.name: Hey! Everyone, run!

rows.label: qst202717_0080
rows.name: Get out of here right now!

rows.label: qst202717_0090
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Damn it. What's going on?

rows.label: qst202717_0100
rows.name:
Everyone's hypnotized.
They can't hear us.

rows.label: qst202717_0110
rows.name: Who are you, mo?

rows.label: qst202717_0120
rows.name:
We are in the middle of a sacred ritual.
No one is allowed to interfere, mo.

rows.label: qst202717_0130
rows.name: What's so sacred about this ritual?

rows.label: qst202717_0140
rows.name:
If you keep this up,
you'll all be killed.

rows.label: qst202717_0150
rows.name: Wonderful.

rows.label: qst202717_0160
rows.name:
That is precisely the prelude
to a new beginning, mo.

rows.label: qst202717_0170
rows.name:
This one's garbage...[ML:Dash ] He's
completely full of himself.

rows.label: qst202717_0180
rows.name: Everyone, over there.

rows.label: qst202717_0190
rows.name:
Is that the delinquent
girl we were looking for?

rows.label: qst202717_0200
rows.name: I feel for you, but I'm taking her back.

rows.label: qst202717_0210
rows.name:
That would be a problem, mo. The ritual
is about to reach its climax, mo.

rows.label: qst202717_0220
rows.name:
She must become a sacrifice
to the Lord of Darkness, mo.

rows.label: qst202717_0230
rows.name: I won't let you.

rows.label: qst202717_0240
rows.name:
So you insist on defying
us, mo. Very well, mo.

rows.label: qst202717_0250
rows.name:
You too will become a sacrifice
for the new world, mo.

rows.label: qst202717_0260
rows.name:
Behold, mo! The descent of
our Lord of Darkness, mo!

rows.label: qst202717_0270
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Mo mo!

rows.label: qst202717_0280
rows.name:
Now, Lord of Darkness, mo! Destroy
this world as you please...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202717_0290
rows.name: Mo!

rows.label: qst202717_0300
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?!

rows.label: qst202717_0310
rows.name: Everyone!

rows.label: qst202717_0320
rows.name:
We'll defeat this rampaging piece
of crap and rescue everyone.

rows.label: qst202717_0330
rows.name: I agree, but...[ML:Dash ] it looks tough.

rows.label: qst202717_0340
rows.name: But we have to do it.

rows.label: qst202717_0350
rows.name:
If we leave it be, not just the Nopon,
but the world might be destroyed.

rows.label: qst202717_0360
rows.name:
Hehe...[ML:Dash ] don't worry. I
am a [System:Ruby rt=Blade of the Dark element]ruler of darkness[/System:Ruby].

rows.label: qst202717_0370
rows.name:
My right hand has been
itching for a while.

rows.label: qst202717_0380
rows.name: I'll show you where you truly belong.

rows.label: qst202717_0390
rows.name: Return to the [System:Ruby rt=Fluch Gef√§ngnis]Cursed Prison[/System:Ruby]!
